表格订单主表的代码预览

drop table if exists ORDER_BASEINFO;

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: ORDER_BASEINFO */
/*==============================================================*/
create table ORDER_BASEINFO
(
ORDER_ID varchar(12) not null,
CUST_CELLPHONE char(11) not null,
CUST_REALNAME varchar(256),
CUST_ID_CARD_NO varchar(18),
ORDER_STATUS char(2) not null,
IS_ASSURE bit not null default 0,
COMPANY_ID char(6),
COMPANY_NAME varchar(64),
ITEM_CODE char(4),
ITEM_NAME varchar(128),
TOTAL_PERIOD int(2),
ORDER_AMOUNT decimal(10,2),
CONTRACT_ID varchar(18),
CREATE_TIME datetime not null default CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
UPDATETIME datetime not null default CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
primary key (ORDER_ID)
);
